    {
      "id": "PopularPost351944",
      "post_content": "@Shane: Yes, it'd be better. And it'd be broken as hell.  \n  \nNow, onto theory crafting time: [Clone](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Clone). A [Clone](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Clone) that copies Epochrasite should get the resurrection clause, but after it's exiled it ceases to be a copy of Epochrasite. However, because of the wording of Epochrasite's resurrection clause it should still gain Suspend 3. However, it comes into play as a Clone which mean it can copy something else!  \n  \nBonus points: [Clone](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Clone) comes into play from exile and copies Epochrasite. It comes into play as a copy, but from exile, therefore it gets the 3 +1/+1 counters. Huzzah, clone hilarity!",
      "posted_by": "DoragonShinzui",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost351944\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">@Shane: Yes, it'd be better. And it'd be broken as hell.<br/><br/>Now, onto theory crafting time: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Clone\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Clone\">Clone</a>. A <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Clone\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Clone\">Clone</a> that copies Epochrasite should get the resurrection clause, but after it's exiled it ceases to be a copy of Epochrasite. However, because of the wording of Epochrasite's resurrection clause it should still gain Suspend 3. However, it comes into play as a Clone which mean it can copy something else!<br/><br/>Bonus points: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Clone\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Clone\">Clone</a> comes into play from exile and copies Epochrasite. It comes into play as a copy, but from exile, therefore it gets the 3 +1/+1 counters. Huzzah, clone hilarity!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '351944'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy79844\">DoragonShinzui</span>\r\n                                (11/19/2013 9:25:48 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"